title: Extending the Habari Sidebar
tags:
  - blog
  - habari
id: 34
categories:
  - Software
date: 2010-06-26 00:10:13
---

Habari's sidebar (in K2) is very minimal. The following plug-ins provide much needed site-navigation:> [Fluffytag](http://habariproject.org/dist/plugins/fluffytag/) shows a fluffy cloud of tags.
> [monthly_archives](http://habariproject.org/dist/plugins/monthly_archives/) shows archives grouped by month.

To display output from both plug-ins, make the following changes to `sidebar.php`:
{% codeblock lang:diff %}

*** system/themes/k2/sidebar.php 2010-06-21 22:15:10.587118909 +0800
--- user/themes/k2/sidebar.php 2010-06-26 14:52:35.928366633 +0800
***************
*** 13,18 ****
--- 13,28 ----

  &lt;?php $theme-&gt;area( 'sidebar' ); ?&gt;

+ &lt;div class=&quot;sb-archives&quot;&gt;
+ &lt;h2&gt;&lt;?php _e('Archives'); ?&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
+ &lt;?php $theme-&gt;monthly_archives ( '0','N' ); ?&gt;
+ &lt;/div&gt;
+
+ &lt;div class=&quot;sb-tags&quot;&gt;
+ &lt;h2&gt;&lt;?php _e('Tags'); ?&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
+ &lt;?php $theme-&gt;fluffytag(); ?&gt;
+ &lt;/div&gt;
+
   &lt;div class=&quot;sb-user&quot;&gt;
   &lt;h2&gt;&lt;?php _e('User'); ?&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;?php $theme-&gt;display ( 'loginform' ); ?&gt;
{% endcodeblock %}


Fluffytag's appearance was slightly modified with the following changes:
{% codeblock lang:diff %}

Index: fluffytag.css
===================================================================
--- fluffytag.css (revision 3226)
+++ fluffytag.css (working copy)
@@ -7,11 +7,10 @@
 #fluffytag li a {
  margin: 0px;
  line-height: 34px;
- color: #000;
+ color: #CCCCCC;
 }
 #fluffytag li a:hover {
- background: #000;
- color: #fff;
+ color: #444444;
 }
 #fluffytag .step-1 a {
  font-size: 1.0em;
@@ -42,4 +41,4 @@
 }
 #fluffytag .step-10 a {
  font-size: 2.8em;
-}
\ No newline at end of file
+}
{% endcodeblock %}
